<item>
            <title>[ENTESB-3414] Fuse Integration Pack is missing several Drools+jBPM artifacts</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/ENTESB-3414</link>
                <project id="12314570" key="ENTESB">JBoss Fuse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Fuse integration pack is missing several artifacts which were included in the previous version of Integration pack [1] already published with BxMS 6.1.x:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;org.drools/drools-osgi-integration/6.2.0.Final-redhat-6&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;org.kie/jbpm-workitems-camel/6.2.0.Final-redhat-6&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;org.kie/kie-camel/6.2.0.Final-redhat-6&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;[1] &lt;a href=&quot;http://dev138.mw.lab.eng.bos.redhat.com/candidate/brms-6.1.0.CR2/jboss-brms-bpmsuite-6.1.0.GA-integration-pack.zip&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://dev138.mw.lab.eng.bos.redhat.com/candidate/brms-6.1.0.CR2/jboss-brms-bpmsuite-6.1.0.GA-integration-pack.zip&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;please note that the zip contains drools-karaf-features xml file bundled in a jar which is a known issue (the xml file should be there instead)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;please note that the current version of the artifacts is 6.2.0.Final-redhat-6, I have linked the Integration pack from GA for easier reference, the latest content is bundled within a patch zip at [2]&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;[2] &lt;a href=&quot;http://dev138.mw.lab.eng.bos.redhat.com/candidate/brms-6.1.1.CR2/20150529/jboss-brms-6.1.1-patch.zip&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://dev138.mw.lab.eng.bos.redhat.com/candidate/brms-6.1.1.CR2/20150529/jboss-brms-6.1.1-patch.zip&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
